# Trinity Protocol Evolution Plan

This plan outlines the steps to implement the improvements proposed in the Trinity Protocol Roadmap.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This plan introduces a centralized `trinity` CLI and [Makefile](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/Makefile) which will become the standard entry points for all project repositories. This will change the workflow for autonomous agents.

