## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

- `make validate` to run JudgeGuard and ProcessGuard checks.
- Test `trinity init` on a legacy script to verify auto-manifest generation.

### Manual Verification

- Verify that `trinity train` correctly invokes the appropriate training script.
- Review [GUARD_LOG.md](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/GUARD_LOG.md) for quality assurance.
